<h2>
    Enable votes in a conference
    <%= link_to "Â¶", "#enable-votes-in-a-conference", name: "enable-votes-in-a-conference" %>
</h2>

<p>
    <strong>Endpoint:</strong>
    <code>POST</code>
    <code>/api/conferences/:id/enable_voting</code>
</p>

<p>
  This endpoint enables the voting of the specified conference. The
  <code>:id</code>
  parameter may be the numeric ID or the slug from a conference.
</p>

<div class="window-orange">
    <div class="window-title-orange pure-g">
        <div class="pure-u-1">
            <i class="fa fa-warning fa-2x fa-fw"></i>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="window-content">
        <span>
            This endpoint requires authentication by means of a token sent in the
            HTTP header (
            <code>token</code>
            ). This token can be generated through the admin panel.
        </span>
    </div>
</div>

<p>
    <strong>Example:</strong>
    <code>POST</code>
    <code><%= base_url %>/conferences/5/enable_voting</code>
    or
    <code><%= base_url %>/conferences/xxviii-jornadas-tecnicas-del-gul/enable_voting</code>
</p>
